
An online Hotel Booking and Management System using PHP, MySQL, HTML5 and CSS. This was made to demonstrate web-designing and database-programming skills.

Features:

    Basic Forms like Sign-Up and Sign-In.
    Four different room types and limited rooms.
    Algorithm to check room availability between entered dates.
    Keep record of previous bookings and payment details of all users.
    Save previous due, advance payment and current due.


Running the Project:

    Install XAMPP
    Copy 'bookHotel' folder to htdocs
    Run XAMPP and open the web page using browser - localhost/bookHotel/index.php


